	  - Bump font version to 2.01.
	* arundina/ArundinaSerif*.sfd:
	  - Set TTF Preferred Family to "Arundina Serif".
	  - Bump font version to 3.01.

	This reverts commit 5fd33990b56ad50894d3faebc30fe60c243e3474
	as a result.

